|-----------------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------|-------------------|-----------------------------|-----------------------------|
| Year                              | The plafond is calculated for the year entered in this field                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                          |                  |                   |                             |                             |
| Plafond Amount (LCY)              | Plafond amount for the current year                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                   |                  |                   |                             |                             |
